section.para:
Creating autoloaders is a fairly trivial task, all that is needed 
is that an autoloader implement Zym_Loader_Autoload_Interface;
however, Zend_Loader does not require this itself.

While Zend_Loader only requires that a class have an autoload($class)
function that is compatible with spl_autoload_register(),
it was Zym's goal to standardize this with an interface.
